EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This code is provided primarily for educational purposes to teach concepts in:
- Molecular dynamics simulation
- Computational physics
- Numerical methods
- Scientific computing with MATLAB

The implementation prioritizes clarity and pedagogical value over performance.
For production use, consider optimized molecular dynamics packages.
